description.en: NVZN Token is blockchain’s ability to give unbreakable lifecycle tracking of waste, which will be useful when providing audit and accountability, with government regulators, and to create a token that is helping solve the energy problem by helping fund green energy projects. Creating a domino effect of ease, for multiple world controversies such as, climate change, seismic activity, etc.
